section.section:
The Department or a person designated by the Department shall issue a complimentary hunting license each year to an individual who:
Has been authorized by the Department to give the course of instruction in conservation and in competency and safety in the handling of firearms under subsection (b) of this section;
Has completed at least 5 years of service as an instructor of this course;
Maintains active certification as an instructor of this course;
Has taught two hunter safety courses during the fiscal year preceding the issuance of the license; and
Has indicated to the Department an interest in receiving a complimentary hunting license.
